(42, 4, 21, 44, 3, 18, 18, 'this scripture fulfilled', 'Fulfillment of Prophecy', 'This connection highlights the theme of fulfillment in both passages. Luke emphasizes the immediate fulfillment of scripture in Jesus, while Acts refers to the broader prophetic fulfillment concerning Christ''s suffering.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 4, 21, 42, 10, 23, 24, 'this scripture fulfilled in your ears', 'Fulfillment of Prophecy', 'This connection highlights the fulfillment of scripture and the significance of witnessing divine revelation. Both passages emphasize the blessedness of seeing and hearing the truths that were longed for by prophets and kings.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 4, 21, 44, 2, 16, 18, 'This day is this scripture fulfilled', 'Fulfillment of Prophecy', 'This connection highlights the theme of fulfillment, as both passages emphasize the realization of God''s promises. Luke 4:21 declares the fulfillment of scripture, while Acts 2:16-18 cites the prophecy of Joel being realized through the outpouring of the Spirit.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
