(42, 4, 22, 40, 13, 54, 56, 'Is not this Joseph’s son?', 'Connection of Jesus'' Identity', 'Both passages emphasize the astonishment of the people regarding Jesus'' wisdom and works, questioning his identity as the son of a carpenter or Joseph. This connection highlights the familiarity of Jesus'' background and the surprise at his teachings.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
